WEBVTT

00:07.508 --> 00:09.710
‐ Previously
on "Resident Alien"...

00:10.844 --> 00:11.645
‐ Where did you say you
actually saw the alien, again?

00:12.713 --> 00:13.380
‐ You can read about that
in the book I'm writing.

00:14.014 --> 00:15.215
[grunting]
[bone crunches]

00:16.083 --> 00:18.018
‐ You killed him?
Those aren't our orders!

00:18.051 --> 00:20.153
‐ Looks like you and I
have different orders.

00:20.187 --> 00:22.422
‐ Hi. My son ran
out of your office...

00:22.456 --> 00:23.524
[Max yelling]
A few days ago.

00:23.557 --> 00:25.325
He told me you're an alien.

00:25.359 --> 00:27.394
He even convinced the deputy
to draw this.

00:27.427 --> 00:29.396
[children laughing]

00:29.429 --> 00:30.964
‐ You want to make fun
of me too?

00:30.998 --> 00:34.268
‐ No. Because I believe you.

00:34.301 --> 00:35.569
‐ Hey, hey.
‐ Hi!

00:35.602 --> 00:36.670
‐ You guys want some?

00:36.703 --> 00:37.671
‐ Those are Sam's.

00:37.704 --> 00:40.040
This prescription was written
after he died.

00:40.073 --> 00:42.142
Jay?

00:42.175 --> 00:44.177
When I was 16, I got pregnant.

00:44.211 --> 00:45.612
I gave the baby up
for adoption.

00:46.079 --> 00:48.382
[dramatic music]

00:48.515 --> 00:49.650
‐ There's another dead body.

00:49.783 --> 00:52.119
‐ That foot belongs
to the guy I killed.

00:52.219 --> 00:53.654
Why are you on my beach?

00:53.787 --> 00:55.322
‐ Rest of that body's got to be
out there somewhere.

00:55.455 --> 00:56.657
We're searching
this entire lake.

00:57.157 --> 00:59.393
♪ ♪

00:59.526 --> 01:02.396
[Gary Portnoy's "Where
Everybody Knows Your Name"]

01:02.529 --> 01:05.098
♪ ♪

